    <arm_group_label>Perampanel</arm_group_label>
    <description>Participants receiving perampanel tablets, orally according to prescribing information and the treating physician's clinical judgment will be observed prospectively for up to 6 months or participant withdrawal, whichever occurs first.</description>
  </arm_group>
